{
  "stem": "22086.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But probably, they said that Bella should have never done it in their heart, or how did she do it for them without everybody around to her not knowing it.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They just couldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Her family really didn't know that we were in their house under the floor when we went out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, you-- he knew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We went out during the night that we are alive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But, but they knew that the sister was in touch.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They knew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was raising a pig for that reason, that she should be able to get more potatoes, and flour, and stuff like that.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She used to bake bread herself every day in a regular small oven in our apartment.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I wanted to say that she didn't have a house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She had a room in her parents' house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And she used to-- and the people that sold her the flour and the potatoes that she went to knew something, because they were people that knew us from before.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they knew that she herself didn't have any money, that the money has to come from the Lippers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- but they never asked her if she knows something about us, or if she-- if we are in contact with her.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They never questioned her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But they told us afterwards that they suspected something.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they helped her, really.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And as far as her family, she had an alibi that she raises a pig.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And, and that's who she buys the flour and the extra potatoes for.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that was very little.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We use to get a loaf of bread every day and just a little soup.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That wasn't much, the minimum.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We, we [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] got free in, in '44.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
